{"word":"Arabians","slug":"arabians","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Arabians</b> Pay tribute to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=14'>2Ch 9:14</a><br/> Pay tribute to Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=11'>2Ch 17:11</a><br/> Invade and defeat Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=17'>2Ch 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=1'>2Ch 22:1</a><br/> Defeated by Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=7'>2Ch 26:7</a><br/> Oppose Nehemiah's rebuilding the walls of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=19'>Neh 2:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=7'>Neh 4:7</a><br/> Commerce of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=21'>Eze 27:21</a><br/> Gospel preached to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=11'>Act 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=17'>Gal 1:17</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=21&verse=17'>Isa 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=11'>Isa 42:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=7'>Isa 60:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=24'>Jer 25:24</a>"}]}